Garey mest OER? SSSR PCT W me ED 1982 HISPANIC SMOKER study tpp s8a - 86Y Prepared by Richena Esposito Strategic Research RB 465964152
summary: Garey grotesquely misused the term "OER" to refer to the European Economic Area. He also used the word "s8a-86Y" for the length of a person's stay in the United States. The term was used to describe the distance from the U.S. to Europe.
